			{
				position[]={5434.2749,75.125999,17871.65};
			};
			title="Research Station?";
			description="Objective 2: Main Research Facility (Ground Level)" \n "Location: Ground level of the central research building." \n "Description: The facility shows signs of struggle, with overturned furniture and bloodstains. A few low-level zombies roam, a mix of guards and scientists." \n "Clue: On a computer in the security office, players access emails between scientists discussing the ""Lazarus Serum"" and its potential effects on reanimation. One email points out a growing risk of ""secondary infections"" and directs anyone needing assistance to the medical lab for serum samples and the potential antidote." \n "Next Objective: Head to the Medical Lab to locate the antidote or any medical insight.";
			id=2882;
			atlOffset=0.00029754639;
		};
